title: Trender's ParaZeit 9/29: Worlds 2022, Stadia, Ginni Thomas, Cybertruck, Dennis Rodman
itunes:title: Trender's ParaZeit 9/29: Worlds 2022, Stadia, Ginni Thomas, Cybertruck, Dennis Rodman
description:
In this edition of Trender's ParaZeit, Miles and DJ Danl discuss the 2022 League of Legends tournament, Google sunsetting Stadia, Ginni Thomas speaking with the 1/6 committee, the famously amphibious Cybertruck, and Dennis Rodman's infamous 48hrs in Vegas being turned into a movie!

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
